<template>
  <header data-bs-theme="dark">

  </header>
</template>
  
<script>
import store from "@/scripts/store";
import router from "@/scripts/router";

export default {
  name: 'Header',
  setup() {
    const logout = () => {
      store.commit('setAccount', 0);
      sessionStorage.removeItem("id");
      router.push({ path: '/' });

    }
    return {logout};
  }
}

</script>

<style scoped>
@import '../assets/css/components/header.css'

</style>
